title: Real Friends Classic: 109 - My Day Off
itunes:title: Real Friends Classic: 109 - My Day Off
description:
We needed a wee break, but we'll be back next week better than ever. This week, we're traveling back, back, back to season one. Donald eulogizes Sam Lloyd, and the guys go deep on their stand-ins. JD is nervous about Turk performing his appendectomy, Elliot attempts to improve her bedside manner, and Dr Cox's mentor becomes a patient at the hospital.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
